Thank you, Great Chief M24. I am now watch duty medicine man. I have eagle carved on rock, bear carved on rock, and snake carved on rock for the more difficult cases. I have yellow ocher in bear fat for body pain. I have many fetish and hold great secrets. I will burn sage in your honor to remove evil spirits from the north.<br><br>
Medicine Man Art<br><br>

